description: The Fund seeks to track the performance of an index composed of international infrastructure companies from both developed and emerging countries. The index provider has decided to discontinue the Macquarie Global Infrastructure 100 index as of 22 May 2017, and as a result the Fund has decided to replace this index with the FTSE Global Core Infrastructure Index. The change will be reflected in the benchmark data.
name: iShares Global Infrastructure UCITS ETF
